{"tid":711055,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《未來戰士》Sarah Connor回歸　61歲蓮達變成咁","createTime":"2018-06-21T08:57:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T12:15:25.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8eb9d1800c9c302ae6259ddd022f39e4e132fae9","tid":711055,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:57:09.000Z","msg":"由荷里活影星阿諾舒華辛力加（Arnold Schwarzenegger）擔正的《未來戰士》（Terminator）系列電影長拍長有，多年來除了阿諾，亦換上不少主角，不過近期開拍的新一集，即系列的第6集，不但有導演占士金馬倫（James Cameron）回歸，更有阿諾的經典女拍檔蓮達咸美頓（Linda Hamilton）再現身大銀幕演「Sarah Connor」！ <br />\n<br />\n蓮達飾演的「Sarah」出現於《未來戰士》頭兩集，是為人類反抗軍領袖John的媽媽，角色打得又睇得，深入民心，事隔17年回歸系列亦令粉絲大為驚喜，而蓮達本周二就於西班牙拍攝《未來戰士6》，角色造型首曝光！61歲的她身形仍然好似以前咁Fit，惟一頭白髮加上老了不少，相信粉絲就未必認得，不過她於片場拎槍的場面就與前作一樣有功架，未知片中是否都有不少動作場面。至於早前做心臟手術出意外的阿諾暫時就未現身片場，似乎仍然休養當中。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.collider.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/terminator-6-linda-hamilton-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.collider.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2Fterminator-6-linda-hamilton-1.png&h=e2166118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.collider.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/terminator-6-linda-hamilton-2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.collider.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2Fterminator-6-linda-hamilton-2.png&h=6c9966fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c1141bb5ace49e056568eafdb66b12e3eccefa1","tid":711055,"uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/06/20/17/4D73F78600000578-5866325-image-m-18_1529511881403.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F17%2F4D73F78600000578-5866325-image-m-18_1529511881403.jpg&h=d9616457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/06/20/17/4D73FE0800000578-5866325-image-a-27_1529512053869.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h